## FAQ

**Is it free?**  
Basic features are completely free. Premium features can be accessed using credits earned through app activities.

**Can I use it offline?**  
Downloaded Bible translations work without internet. Some features like Group Study require a connection.

**Is my data safe?**  
We use Firebase's security systems and collect minimal information. See our Privacy Policy for details.

**What translations are available?**  
We offer KRV, Revised Version, Common Translation, KJV, ASV, WEB, CUV, and more, with ongoing additions.

**How do I create a group?**  
Go to the Groups tab, tap "Create Group," and enter a name and description. You can invite members with an invite code.

